<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customer Service Representative - Australia Workforce</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .job-description {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .calendar {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .apply-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #0077b5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .apply-link:hover {
            background-color: #005f8d;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        input, button {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #27ae60;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #1e8449;
        }
        #selectedDateTime {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Customer Service Representative - Remote Job (Australia Workforce)</h1>

    <div class="job-description">
        <h2>Job Description</h2>
        <p>Australia Workforce is hiring a Customer Service Representative for a remote position. Join our team to provide excellent customer service and resolve client inquiries effectively.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Work remotely from Australia or nearby time zones.</li>
            <li>Handle customer inquiries via phone, email, and chat.</li>
            <li>Provide resolutions with a focus on customer satisfaction.</li>
            <li>Flexible hours with full-time availability required.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="calendar">
        <h2>Schedule Your Application</h2>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="applicationDate">Select Date:</label>
            <input type="date" id="applicationDate" name="applicationDate">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="applicationTime">Select Time:</label>
            <input type="time" id="applicationTime" name="applicationTime">
        </div>
        <button onclick="showSelectedDateTime()">Confirm Application Schedule</button>
        <p id="selectedDateTime"></p>
    </div>

    <a href="https://www.australiaworkforce.com/jobs/customer-service-representative-remote" target="_blank" class="apply-link">
        Apply
